            <lg type="edition">
<l>kaṭaṉaṟintu kālaṅ karutiyiṭaṉaṟin </l>
<l> teṇṇi yuraippāṉ talai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>He is chief (among ambassadors) who understands the proper decorum (before foreign princes), seeks the (proper) occasion, knows the (most suitable) place, and delivers his message after (due) consideration.</l>
            </lg>
